				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "The player is locked in Nettie's lab and has cured themselves before persuading her. Normally, script starts the dialog 'DEN_Apprentice_LockedUp' to react to this, but it can fail if the player is wild shaped for example. This node taken from the dialog 'DEN_CGB_Apprentice' gives the feedback thatNettie is going hostile."
				}
			}
